Payment Methods

Wallets allow you to fund and carry a balance from which your parking fees will be deducted. It can simplify your credit card bill and you can receive possible discounts based on available offers.

Our traditional payment method uses a credit or debit card on file to pay for parking.

If you have a validation coupon, you can use it to pay for your parking fees.

Use PayPal to pay for parking!

        Mobile Verification

        How should we contact you?

        We use your phone number to identify you in our system, so we just need to verify your phone number by sending a 3 digit code to you via text or call.

        Send Code

        We use your e-mail to identify you in our system, so we just need to verify your e-mail by sending a 3 digit code to your e-mail address.
